OL,5, A combination of rising costs and      
OL,6, falling donations is hitting the       
OL,7, incomes of UK hospices, a provider has 
OL,8, told the BBC.                          
OL,10,FHavens Hospices in Essex said it was   
OL,11,Fmaking it harder to meet rising demand 
OL,12,Fat its sites in Southend and Benfleet. 
OL,14,FThe average value of one-off donations 
OL,15,Fto the charity has halved since April  
OL,16,Fand its energy, food and staffing costs
OL,17,Fare soaring, said boss Steve Smith.    
OL,19,FAbout 80% of Havens' income comes from 
OL,20,Fdonations, he added.                   
